00:06:51.080 --> 00:06:53.150
How many-- how many arrows
do you want?

00:06:53.150 --> 00:06:56.540
So the next one, let's say we
did 3 to the power of, to the

00:06:56.540 --> 00:06:58.785
power of, to the power--or
arrow, arrow, arrow, or

00:06:58.785 --> 00:07:01.160
whatever you want
to call this.

00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:02.290
3--

00:07:02.290 --> 00:07:03.540
well that, that--

